original_title: The Golden Age of Porn: Kitten Natividad
overview: Along with Candy Samples and Uschi Digard, Kitten Natividad is one third of the holy trinity of giant breasted women in the 1970's. Discovered by cult giant Russ Meyers, Kitten starred in Meyers "UP" and "Beneath The Valley of The Dolls". In her day she reigned supreme and will always be remembered as a giant by breast lovers everywhere.
title: The Golden Age of Porn: Kitten Natividad
